INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (1,1,'2015-12-05 19:58:04','2015-12-05 11:58:04','Hi\r\n','世界，您好！','','publish','open','open','','hello-world','','','2015-12-10 10:24:48','2015-12-10 02:24:48','',0,'http://115.28.66.199/wordpress-4.3.1/wordpress/?p=1',0,'post','',0),(2,1,'2015-12-05 19:58:04','2015-12-05 11:58:04','这是一个范例页面。它和博客文章不同，因为它的页面位置是固定的，同时会显示于您的博客导航栏（大多数主题中）。大多数人会新增一个“关于”页面向访客介绍自己。它可能类似下面这样：\r\n<blockquote>我是一个很有趣的人，我创建了工厂和庄园。并且，顺便提一下，我的妻子也很好。</blockquote>\r\n……或下面这样：\r\n<blockquote>XYZ装置公司成立于1971年，公司成立以来，我们一直向市民提供高品质的装置。我们位于北京市，有超过2,000名员工，对北京市有着相当大的贡献。</blockquote>\r\n作为一个新的WordPress用户，您可以前往<a href=\"http://115.28.66.199/wordpress-4.3.1/wordpress/wp-admin/\">您的仪表盘</a>删除这个页面，并建立属于您的全新内容。祝您使用愉快！','关于','','trash','closed','open','','aboutme','','','2015-12-10 10:24:06','2015-12-10 02:24:06','',0,'http://115.28.66.199/wordpress-4.3.1/wordpress/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),(4,1,'2015-12-09 08:42:54','2015-12-09 00:42:54','&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWordPress是一个博客平台，和Magento同样使用php开发，安装过程也很相似，同样拥有众多插件，丰富的主题模板，备份转移都比较方便，下面介绍一下如何安装WordPress。\r\n<h2>安装</h2>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>搭建PHP服务器（Linux + Apache + PHP + MySQL）</li>\r\n	<li>从官网下载WordPress源码，解压到虚拟主机Apache服务器的根目录（采用apt-get安装后，默认的根目录是/var/www/html)</li>\r\n	<li>新建一个MySQL数据库（数据库名wordpress，用户名admin，密码123456，主机localhost）</li>\r\n	<li>使用浏览器访问http://{IP:port}/wordpress，既可进入安装界面，选择现在就开始<a href=\"http://115.28.66.199/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/step1.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-25\" src=\"http://115.28.66.199/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/step1.png\" alt=\"step1\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" /></a></li>\r\n	<li>输入第三部的数据库名，用户名，密码，数据库主机，表前缀默认wp_<a href=\"http://115.28.66.199/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/step2.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-27\" src=\"http://115.28.66.199/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/step2.png\" alt=\"step2\" width=\"750\" height=\"534\" /></a></li>\r\n	<li>创建wp.config.php文件，拷贝如下文本，放到wordpress根目录下，点击进行安装<a href=\"http://115.28.66.199/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/step3.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-32\" src=\"http://115.28.66.199/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/step3.png\" alt=\"step3\" width=\"750\" height=\"566\" /></a></li>\r\n	<li>连接数据库成功<a href=\"http://115.28.66.199/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/step4.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-33\" src=\"http://115.28.66.199/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/step4.png\" alt=\"step4\" width=\"750\" height=\"244\" /></a></li>\r\n	<li>填写站点标题，登录wordpress后台的用户名，密码，电子邮件<a href=\"http://115.28.66.199/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/step6.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-34\" src=\"http://115.28.66.199/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/step6.png\" alt=\"step6\" width=\"750\" height=\"533\" /></a></li>\r\n	<li>安装成功<a href=\"http://115.28.66.199/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/step71.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-35\" src=\"http://115.28.66.199/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/step71.png\" alt=\"step7\" width=\"750\" height=\"341\" /></a></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n','WordPress建站','','publish','open','open','','wordpress','','','2016-01-04 10:03:23','2016-01-04 02:03:23','',0,'http://115.28.66.199/wordpress-4.3.1/wordpress/?p=4',0,'post','',0),(5,1,'2015-12-05 20:22:27','2015-12-05 12:22:27','hihihihi','hello world','','trash','open','open','','hello-world-2','','','2015-12-05 20:23:27','2015-12-05 12:23:27','',0,'http://115.28.66.199/wordpress-4.3.1/wordpress/?p=5',0,'post','',0),(6,1,'2015-12-05 20:22:27','2015-12-05 12:22:27','hihihihi','hello world','','inherit','closed','closed','','5-revision-v1','','','2015-12-05 20:22:27','2015-12-05 12:22:27','',5,'http://115.28.66.199/wordpress-4.3.1/wordpress/index.php/2015/12/05/5-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(8,1,'2015-12-07 17:32:19','2015-12-07 09:32:19','<em>我是一个很有趣的人，我创建了工厂和庄园。并且，顺便提一下，我的妻子也很好。</em>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<blockquote>&nbsp;</blockquote>\r\n&nbsp;','关于','','inherit','closed','closed','','2-autosave-v1','','','2015-12-07 17:32:19','2015-12-07 09:32:19','',2,'http://115.28.66.199/index.php/2015/12/07/2-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(10,1,